American /əˈmɛrɪkən/

(Americans) 

1. ADJ An American person or thing belongs to or comes from the United States of America. 美国的; 来自美国的  →  see also Latin American 

例： ...the American ambassador at the United Nations. ...美国驻联合国大使。 

例： ...the influence of American television and movies. ...美国电视和电影产生的影响。 

2. N-COUNT An American is someone who is American. 美国人 

例： The 1990 Nobel Prize for medicine was won by two Americans. 两名美国人获得了1990年度诺贝尔医学奖。

